    He walks onto the bridge, looking around he sees Klus=
ter. He walks over and looks him in the optics.
    "Unicron could be back,=
 as I've said many times," Prime said. "I need to use the ship's scanners."=

    He walks over to the scanner equipment not even bothering to wait for =
an answer.
    "Wow, these are so much better than the Autobot an Decpticon=
 days," Prime said. "Primus, he's not even there. But there is a massive te=
mporal distortion."
